INNER JOIN [Pxp_Categories] AS [p1] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [p1].[Id]

    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p3].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_5
) AS [t0] ON [p].[CreditCardId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Flags] AS [p4] ON [t0].[FlagCardId] = [p4].[Id]

    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[AccountNickname], [p0].[AccountNumber], [p0].[AccountType], [p0].[AgencyNumber], [p0].[BalanceAvailable], [p0].[BankId], [p0].[CreationTime], [p0].[CreatorUserId], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[LastModificationTime], [p0].[LastModifierUserId], [p0].[MainAccount], [p0].[Origin], [p0].[PluggyAccountId], [p0].[PluggyItemId], [p0].[StatusPluggyItem], [p0].[TenantId]
    FROM [Pxp_Accounts] AS [p0]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p0].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_5
) AS [t] ON [p].[AccountId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Banks] AS [p1] ON [t].[BankId] = [p1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Pxp_Flags] AS [p2] ON [p].[FlagCardId] = [p2].[Id]

    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p3].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_3
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[CreditCardId]
WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_1
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t].[Id], [p1].[Id], [p2].[Id], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Pxp_Transactions] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[AccountNickname], [p0].[AccountNumber], [p0].[AccountType], [p0].[AgencyNumber], [p0].[BalanceAvailable], [p0].[BankId], [p0].[CreationTime], [p0].[CreatorUserId], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[LastModificationTime], [p0].[LastModifierUserId], [p0].[MainAccount], [p0].[Origin], [p0].[PluggyAccountId], [p0].[PluggyItemId], [p0].[StatusPluggyItem], [p0].[TenantId]
    FROM [Pxp_Accounts] AS [p0]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p0].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_3
) AS [t] ON [p].[AccountId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Pxp_Categories] AS [p1] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [p1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Banks] AS [p2] ON [t].[BankId] = [p2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p3].[Id], [p3].[AccountId], [p3].[CardName], [p3].[CardNumber], [p3].[CreationTime], [p3].[CreatorUserId], [p3].[DueDay], [p3].[FlagCardId], [p3].[IsActive], [p3].[LastModificationTime], [p3].[LastModifierUserId], [p3].[Limit], [p3].[Origin], [p3].[PluggyCreditCardId], [p3].[PluggyItemId], [p3].[TenantId]
    FROM [Pxp_Cards] AS [p3]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p3].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_5
) AS [t0] ON [p].[CreditCardId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Flags] AS [p4] ON [t0].[FlagCardId] = [p4].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Subcategories] AS [p5] ON [p1].[Id] = [p5].[CategoryId]

FROM [Pxp_Cards] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[AccountNickname], [p0].[AccountNumber], [p0].[AccountType], [p0].[AgencyNumber], [p0].[BalanceAvailable], [p0].[BankId], [p0].[CreationTime], [p0].[CreatorUserId], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[LastModificationTime], [p0].[LastModifierUserId], [p0].[MainAccount], [p0].[Origin], [p0].[PluggyAccountId], [p0].[PluggyItemId], [p0].[StatusPluggyItem], [p0].[TenantId]
    FROM [Pxp_Accounts] AS [p0]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [p].[AccountId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Banks] AS [p1] ON [t].[BankId] = [p1].[Id]

LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Banks] AS [p2] ON [t0].[BankId] = [p2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p3].[Id], [p3].[AccountId], [p3].[CardName], [p3].[CardNumber], [p3].[CreationTime], [p3].[CreatorUserId], [p3].[DueDay], [p3].[FlagCardId], [p3].[IsActive], [p3].[LastModificationTime], [p3].[LastModifierUserId], [p3].[Limit], [p3].[Origin], [p3].[PluggyCreditCardId], [p3].[PluggyItemId], [p3].[TenantId]

) AS [t1] ON [t0].[CreditCardId] = [t1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Flags] AS [p4] ON [t1].[FlagCardId] = [p4].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Pxp_Subcategories] AS [p5] ON [p1].[Id] = [p5].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t0].[Date] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [p1].[Id], [p2].[Id], [t1].[Id], [p4].[Id]
